          <h3 class="brand-heading">Regional centres of excellence and specialism</h3>
          <p>We offer a full range of local hospital and community health services for people in Sheffield as well as specialist hospital services to patients from further afield in our many specialist centres.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag 'hilary.jpg', width: "100%" %>
