          <h3 class="brand-heading">Structured career pathways</h3>
          <p>We pride ourselves in growing talent. A testament to this is that nine out of ten of our top nurses, including our Chief Nurse, have had the majority of their career with us. Because of this, you can be assured of an interesting and diverse career path.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 hidden-sm">
        <%= image_tag 'shu-cantor.jpg', width: "100%" %>
