          <h3 class="brand-heading">Large Research Department</h3>
          <p>From <a href="http://www.sth.nhs.uk/news/news?action=view&amp;newsID=610" alt="news article on A VIRTUAL heart prototype which assesses heart disease better than the naked eye could revolutionise the treatment and assessment of heart disease – saving lives and money.">virtual hearts</a> to
                <a href="http://www.sth.nhs.uk/news/news?action=view&amp;newsID=631" alt="news article on how Sheffield Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust becomes first NHS hospital in country to treat patients with new therapy for wet age-related macular degeneration (wet AMD), the leading cause of blindness in the western world">new therapies tackling the leading cause of blindness</a>, we are
                  always looking to provide world-class care to our patients and
                  research plays a large part in that effort.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 hidden-sm">
        <%= image_tag 'simon.jpg', width: "100%" %>
        <div class="well">
          <h3 class="brand-heading">Modern Foundation Trust with cutting-edge technology</h3>
          <p>Innovation is a core value here at Sheffield Teaching Hospitals so much so that we have just pledged a massive investment into our internal clinical technology in a plan called “Transformation Through Technology”</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6">
        <%= image_tag 'day_centre.jpg', width: "100%" %>
